ALTER PROC [dbo].[ImportDimCategories] AS begin
insert into dbo.DimCategories
(
	MovieCategoryDescription
)
SELECT * FROM (
    select distinct
        Genre
    from extern.catalog
) cleaned_table
WHERE cleaned_table.Genre NOT IN (SELECT MovieCategoryDescription FROM [dbo].[DimCategories])
;
END
GO
